-- Personality: There is not much complexity to her. She is happy, confident and extremely polite. She is a sole minded individual focused entirely on the art of cooking.
-- Background: She grew up watching her father cook. At about 5 she started experimenting with the stove with the help of a ladder. Her parents were worried and especially freaked out after she burned her left hand at six. They banned her from the stove for a year; afterwards she badgered her mother who eventually let her back into the kitchen. She practiced cooking every day when the customers were not around. She soon outclassed her father in cooking skills and took over as the cook. After her mother passed away, they make just enough money to get by, but it's a happy life, especially for Linda who has her father and the esteem of being famous as the best cook in Cadomyr.

